# pycharm

# customize

1 download ideavim
2 vimrc
3 光标
  Settings -> Editor -> General -> Appearance -> Use Block Caret
4 quickfix-wrap
  View -> Active Editor -> Use Soft Wraps

5 pip配置文件
  %APPDATA%\pip\pip.ini
  pip list --format=columns

http://www.10tiao.com/html/502/201609/2653283804/1.html
http://zhibimo.com/read/xiaolai/growth/attribution-fallacy.html

# reduce memo usgae

1 File -> setting -> 关插件
2 File -> power-save-mode
3 换个8G的机器吧，时间才是最贵的

# shortcut

F4        定义
F5        run
Alt-F5    run...

# 窗口导航

左下角口  toggle导航框，通过相应 Alt-Num toggle细目
Alt-1     Project/Nerdtree
Alt-2     收藏夹
Alt-4     Debug窗/Quickfix
Alt-7     Structure/Tlist
Alt-F12   Dos-shell

